{"title_page": "List of performers at the Montreux Jazz Festival", "text_new": "{{Update|date=May 2019}}\n{{short description|Wikimedia list article}}\n__FORCETOC__\n{{TOC limit|2}}\nThis is a list of artists that have performed at the [[Montreux Jazz Festival]].\n<!-- the listings below were script-generated in october 2016 -->\n<!-- distinct artists at generation time: 1394 -->\n<!-- Notes to editors:\n   1. the artist name should only be wikilinked on its first appearance on this page, do not link every occurrence (WP:OVERLINK)\n   2. the initial list was automatically generated by a crawler script over the festival's website. It probably has a few errors, such\n      as tribute concerts being listed as appearances by the actual artist. These will require manual verification.\n-->\n\n==Artist performances by year==\n=== 1967 ===\nThe 1967 edition of the festival featured performances of three artists:<ref name=lineup1967/>\n{{colbegin|colwidth=15em}}\n* [[Charles Lloyd (jazz musician)|Charles Lloyd]]\n* [[Jack DeJohnette]]\n* [[Keith Jarrett]]\n{{colend}}\n\n=== 1968 ===\nThe 1968 edition of the festival featured performances of four artists:<ref name=lineup1968/>\n{{colbegin|colwidth=15em}}\n* [[Bill Evans]]\n* [[Eddie G\u00f3mez]]\n* Jack DeJohnette\n* [[Nina Simone]]\n{{colend}}\n\n=== 1969 ===\nThe 1969 edition of the festival featured performances of seven artists:<ref name=lineup1969/>\n{{colbegin|colwidth=15em}}\n* [[Clark Terry]]\n* [[Colosseum (band)|Colosseum]]\n* [[Eddie Harris]]\n* [[Ella Fitzgerald]]\n* [[George Gruntz]]\n* [[Les McCann]]\n* [[Ten Years After]]\n{{colend}}\n\n=== 1970 ===\nThe 1970 edition of the festival featured performances of 11 artists:<ref name=lineup1970/>\n{{colbegin|colwidth=15em}}\n* Bill Evans\n* [[Carlos Santana]]\n* [[Champion Jack Dupree]]\n* Clark Terry\n* Eddie G\u00f3mez\n* George Gruntz\n* [[Gerry Mulligan]]\n* [[Herbie Mann]]\n* [[Junior Mance]]\n* [[Sadao Watanabe (musician)|Sadao Watanabe]]\n* [[Stone the Crows]]