wax]]\n*Superwak Clique\n*[[Tash Sultana]]\n*[[The Bloody Beetroots]]\n*[[The Lemon Twigs]]\n*[[The New Power Generation]]\n*[[Theo Croker]]\n*Tia Brazda\n*[[Tom Jones (singer)|Tom Jones]]\n*[[Usher (musician)|Usher]] and [[The Roots]]\n*[[Whitney (band)|Whitney]]\n*[[Wolfgang Muthspiel]]\n*Youngr\n{{colend}}\n\n==Artists with most performances==\n=== 27 times ===\n* Herbie Hancock <small>(1979, 1981, 1983, 1986{{ndash}}1994, 1996{{ndash}}1999, 2001, 2002, 2004, 2006, 2008{{ndash}}2012, 2014, 2015)</small>\n\n=== 21 times ===\n* B.B. King <small>(1979, 1980, 1982, 1984, 1987, 1989{{ndash}}1991, 1993, 1995, 1997{{ndash}}2002, 2004{{ndash}}2006, 2009, 2011)</small>\n\n=== 18 times ===\n* George Duke <small>(1976, 1977, 1986{{ndash}}1989, 1991{{ndash}}1993, 1996{{ndash}}2001, 2005, 2006, 2009)</small>\n* John McLaughlin <small>(1974, 1976{{ndash}}1978, 1981, 1984, 1987, 1993, 1995, 1996, 1998, 1999, 2001, 2009{{ndash}}2012, 2015)</small>\n* Van Morrison <small>(1974, 1980, 1984, 1989, 1990, 1994{{ndash}}1999, 2001, 2003, 2004, 2006, 2007, 2012, 2014)</small>\n\n=== 17 times ===\n* Al Jarreau <small>(1976, 1979{{ndash}}1981, 1986, 1990, 1991, 1993, 1996, 1998, 2000, 2002, 2004, 2006, 2007, 2010, 2015)</small>\n\n=== 16 times ===\n* George Benson <small>(1986, 1988{{ndash}}1991, 1995, 1996, 1998, 2000, 2003, 2005, 2007, 2009, 2011, 2013, 2015)</small>\n\n=== 15 times ===\n* David Sanborn <small>(1981, 1984, 1986, 1988, 1990, 1991, 1993, 1996, 1997, 1999, 2000, 2002, 2009, 2011, 2015)</small>\n\n=== 14 times ===\n* Monty Alexander <small>(1976, 1977, 1981, 1984, 1987, 1988, 1993{{ndash}}1995, 1997, 2008, 2009, 2011, 2014)</small>\n\n=== 13 times ===\n* Gilberto Gil <small>(1978, 1982, 1986, 1991, 1993, 1997, 1998, 2001, 2003, 2006, 2008, 2012, 2015)</small>\n* John Scofield <small>(1975, 1976, 1984{{ndash}}1986, 1993, 1994, 1997, 2002, 2004, 2007, 2009, 2014)</small>\n* Stanley Clarke <small>(1972, 1977, 1980, 1988, 1989, 1991, 1994, 1999, 2005, 2006, 2008, 2009, 2011)</s