 Moody (saxophonist)|James Moody]]\n* John McLaughlin\n* Larry Carlton\n* Larry Coryell\n* [[Marcus Miller]]\n* McCoy Tyner\n* [[Mike Oldfield]]\n* Monty Alexander\n* Nina Simone\n* Oscar Peterson\n* [[Rodger Fox]]\n* [[Randy Crawford]]\n* [[Robben Ford]]\n* Stray Cats\n* Terry Clarke\n{{colend}}\n\n=== 1982 ===\nThe 1982 edition of the festival featured performances of 22 artists:<ref name=lineup1982/>\n{{colbegin|colwidth=15em}}\n* [[Alceu Valen\u00e7a]]\n* B.B. King\n* Billy Cobham\n* [[Bobby McFerrin]]\n* Claude Nobs\n* [[Dean Brown (guitarist)|Dean Brown]]\n* Didier Lockwood\n* Dizzy Gillespie\n* Eddie G\u00f3mez\n* Fran\u00e7ois Lindemann\n* Gilberto Gil\n* [[Jackson Browne]]\n* Jimmy Cliff\n* [[Joe Sample]]\n* [[Larry Graham]]\n* Milton Nascimento\n* [[Ney Matogrosso]]\n* [[Rickie Lee Jones]]\n* [[Stevie Ray Vaughan]]\n* [[Sugar Blue]]\n* The Crusaders\n* Crossfire\n{{colend}}\n\n=== 1983 ===\nThe 1983 edition of the festival featured performances of 21 artists:<ref name=lineup1983/>\n{{colbegin|colwidth=15em}}\n* Art Blakey And The Jazz Messengers\n* [[Bill Laswell]]\n* Billy Cobham\n* Buddy Guy\n* [[Caetano Veloso]]\n* Charles Lloyd\n* Clark Terry\n* Claude Nobs\n* Fats Domino\n* [[Freddie Hubbard]]\n* Herbie Hancock\n* Herbie Mann\n* [[John Lee Hooker]]\n* [[Jo\u00e3o Bosco]]\n* [[Kenny Barron]]\n* Ney Matogrosso\n* [[Pino Daniele]]\n* Rickie Lee Jones\n* Sugar Blue\n* Willie Dixon\n* Pyramid\n* Ronald Shannon Jackson and the Decoding Society\n{{colend}}\n\n=== 1984 ===\nThe 1984 edition of the festival featured performances of 22 artists:<ref name=lineup1984/>\n{{colbegin|colwidth=15em}}\n* B.B. King\n* Bill Evans\n* Bobby McFerrin\n* [[Chris Rea]]\n* [[Darryl Jones]]\n* David Sanborn\n* Dee Dee Bridgewater\n* Elba Ramalho\n* Freddie Hubbard\n* [[Gianna Nannini]]\n* John McLaughlin\n* John Scofield\n* Klaus Doldinger\n* Miles Davis\n* Monty Alexander\n* [[Paco De Lucia]]\n* Rickie Lee Jones\n* [[Robert Cray]]\n* [[Sade (band)|Sade]]\n* [[Stephan Eicher]]\