hard Galliano\n* [[Slayer]]\n* [[Soulfly]]\n* [[Speedy J]]\n* Stephan Eicher\n* Terri Lyne Carrington\n* [[The Matthew Herbert Big Band]]\n* [[The Notwist]]\n* [[Thomas Dutronc]]\n* [[UB40]]\n* Us3\n* [[Wanda S\u00e1]]\n* [[Watcha]]\n* Wayne Shorter\n* Youssou N'Dour\n{{colend}}\n\n=== 2003 ===\nThe 2003 edition of the festival featured performances of 60 artists:<ref name=lineup2003/>\n{{colbegin|colwidth=15em}}\n* Asher Selector\n* [[Baptiste Trotignon Trio]]\n* [[Beth Orton]]\n* Blackalicious\n* [[Brendan Benson]]\n* Chico Cesar\n* [[Craig David]]\n* [[Cypress Hill]]\n* [[Echoboy]]\n* [[Falamansa]]\n* George Benson\n* Gilberto Gil\n* Goldfrapp\n* [[Herbert Gr\u00f6nemeyer]]\n* Jacky Terrasson\n* [[Jair Oliveira]]\n* Jamiroquai\n* [[Jethro Tull (band)|Jethro Tull]]\n* [[Jimi Tenor & Big Band]]\n* Joe Jackson\n* Joe Sample\n* Laurent Garnier\n* [[Laurie Anderson]]\n* [[Lockdown Project]]\n* Maria Beth\u00e2nia\n* [[Marius Vernescu]]\n* [[Masha]]\n* [[Mercan Dede]]\n* [[Michel Jonasz]]\n* Mick Hucknall\n* Mirko Loko\n* [[Mogwai]]\n* [[Nada Surf]]\n* Natalie Cole\n* Noa\n* Pierre Audetat\n* [[Prince Alla]]\n* [[Radiohead]]\n* Randy Crawford\n* [[Ray Parker Jr.]]\n* Richard Galliano\n* Simply Red\n* [[Stereophonics]]\n* [[Susheela Raman]]\n* [[The Blues Brothers]]\n* The Crusaders\n* [[The Flaming Lips]]\n* The Pretenders\n* [[The Rapture (band)|The Rapture]]\n* The Roots\n* [[Tom McRae]]\n* Tony Bennett\n* Tricky\n* Tuck & Patti\n* [[Turin Brakes]]\n* Van Morrison\n* [[Vivian (band)|Vivian]]\n* [[Yes (band)|Yes]]\n* ZZ Top\n* [[Zorg (band)|Zorg]]\n{{colend}}\n\n=== 2004 ===\nThe 2004 edition of the festival featured performances of 105 artists:<ref name=lineup2004/>\n{{colbegin|colwidth=15em}}\n* [[!!!]]\n* [[16 Horsepower]]\n* Air\n* Al Jarreau\n* [[Alicia Keys]]\n* [[Amp Fiddler]]\n* Andr\u00e9 Ceccarelli\n* Ang\u00e9lique Kidjo\n* [[Archive]]\n* Asher Selector\n* [[Avril (Fr\u00e9d\u00e9ric Magnon)|Avril]]\n* B.B. King\n* [[Bang Gang]]\n* Barbara Hendricks\n* [[Bl