ois]]\n[[Category:Suicides by firearm in Idaho]]\n[[Category:Survivors of aviation accidents or incidents]]\n[[Category:American anti-fascists]]\n[[Category:American male essayists]]\n[[Category:American male short story writers]]\n[[Category:People from Ketchum, Idaho]]\n[[Category:20th-century American journalists]]\n[[Category:20th-century American male writers]]\n[[Category:Journalists who committed suicide]]\n[[Category:Male suicides]]\n[[Category:Novelists from Illinois]]\n[[Category:Catholics from Illinois]]\n[[Category:Catholics from Idaho]]\n[[Category:20th-century essayists]]\n", "name_user": "Victoriaearle", "label": "safe", "comment": "\u2192\u200eWorld War I:fmt", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ernest_Hemingway"}
